      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved motorcar, currently maintained in showroom condition. Every aspect of this vehicle\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine, smoke-free interior\u2014reflects a standard of care rarely seen in the pre-owned market. This represents a premier opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and mechanical integrity.",
